org.openadaptor.util
Class Application

java.lang.Object
  org.openadaptor.util.Application
All Implemented Interfaces:
IComponent, IRegistrationCallbackListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
Adaptor
public class Application
extends java.lang.Object
implements IComponent, IRegistrationCallbackListener

core functionality that is desirable for applications, outputs license, loads build properties and if configured posts all the system properties to a url. All the work is done in the constructor, so can be subclassed or instantiated by top level application class (such as an adaptor).
